1》及《早辰。早晨》。王牌節目《鏗鏘集》及《議事論事》料獲保留......<br />\n<br />\n另一港台中人表示，整頓後的公共事務組，預料只餘三個節目，除《鏗鏘集》和《議事論事》外，《城市論壇》料「有得留低」。至於傳出會被停播的《視點31》和《早辰。早晨》，則未清楚「大限」，但估計大整頓會是下月中開展，因屆時已遞信的公共事務組高層陸續離職......"},{"pid":"f21c84c20257af20b25d63b18bc8a90bfa10cf85","tid":2501366,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d8179eb3d30faaa14753e64d53b9b4c56287356","tid":2501366,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a3a93463da99a39e31eb1c0536e18ab47ff061c","tid":2501366,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"問他「點解要搶我枝警棍」。<br />\n用中文問?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"盤問佢用英文讀出警棍 警察 先，唔識的話姐係之前係假口供"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"police stick<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95897e8febe60b7e2b83279503f5ed79593d64ae","tid":2501366,"uid":267167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e43466c507876a8f4430bab47b9a67cddb1a0ccc","tid":2501366,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"呢隻賤畜d英文衰到可以疑點利益歸於被告<br />\n可以判無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"不過而家法治已死<br />\n唔會再有疑點利益歸於被告"},{"pid":"1bc3fcff898d481f4a7711f9d22109fd7e7b0b8e","tid":2501366,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"Leave the hand<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653ad45692220451b49f1e7bfd118422db810918","tid":2501366,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":